          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " After the reaction target a 4 Tm",
                "superconducting magnet was used to bend by 43 deg and",
                "analyse the emitted charged particles. Particles were",
                "identified by series of energy and position sensitive",
                "detectors in focal plane."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Forward focused neutrons were detected using",
                "Modular Neutron Array (MoNA), placed 6.05 m from the",
                "target. MoNA consists of 144 individual detector",
                "modules. Each module is based on a block of BC-408",
                "plastic scintillator measuring 200 x 10 x 10 cm3."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Charged particle detectors and MoNA array provided",
                "relativistic four-momentum vectors for 24-O nuclei",
                "and neutrons, which were used to calculate the decay",
                "energy of two- and three-body systems."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The primary beam of 140 MeV/A 48Ca bombarded a 1316",
                "mg/cm2 9Be production target. The secondary beam 27F",
                "with an energy of 82 MeV/A was separated from the",
                "other reaction products and the primary beam using",
                "the A1900 fragment separator. The 27F component of",
                "the secondary beam was 7%. The main contaminant was",
                "30Na. The 27F fragments were identified event by",
                "event through the time of flight"
              ]
            }
          ],
